########################
# *****  KEEP RULES  *****
#  These reopen just the tiny bits you still need.
########################

# — C# source & its meta
!**/*.cs
!**/*.cs.meta

# — ScriptableObjects (& their meta) – .asset is also used for
#   lots of other things, but we can’t distinguish extension-wise,
#   so leave it tracked.  Delete any unwanted .asset files manually.
!**/*.asset
!**/*.asset.meta

# — Assembly Definition files (handy, tiny JSON)
!**/*.asmdef
!**/*.asmdef.meta

# — Unity meta files in general (they’re all a few KB)
!**/*.meta

# — Minimal project settings so others can open the project
!/ProjectSettings/ProjectVersion.txt
!/ProjectSettings/EditorBuildSettings.asset

